 SPONSORSHIP, TO ENCOURAGE HONG KONG YOUTH TO STUDY AND WORK IN CANADA<br />\n<br />\n* CANADA SAYS NEW MEASURES IN RESPONSE TO IMPLEMENTATION OF NATIONAL SECURITY LAW IN HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n* CANADA'S IMMIGRATION MINISTER INTERVIEW: HOPES HONG KONG YOUTH WILL SEE NEW IMMIGRATION RULES AS AN OPPORTUNITY<br />\n<br />\n* CANADA'S IMMIGRATION MINISTER INTERVIEW: TODAY'S ANNOUNCEMENT SET AGAINST BACKDROP OF GRAVELY CONCERNING DEVELOPMENTS IN HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n* CANADA'S IMMIGRATION MINISTER, IN A REUTERS INTERVIEW, SAYS CHARGES FOR BREECHING CHINA'S NATIONAL SECURITY LAW WILL NOT DISQUALIFY ANYONE SEEKING ASYLUM, PERMANENT RESIDENCY OR OTHER PERMITS IN CANADA Source text for Eikon: (Reporting by Steve Scherer)<br />\n<br />\nSource: Reuters"},{"pid":"f6664f2344da087359303b0b5370e0d1dd6a3d9a","tid":2283624,"uid":3212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:30:19.000Z","msg":"讀hku有鬼妹屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1768c950db38879eebf8c68412581da7dffb41","tid":2283624,"uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"大學生可以去加拿大發展"},{"pid":"a7b39482324dbdb33c02bf14a2ad7df75fa62b0c","tid":2283624,"uid":60366,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"1) Three-year open work permit to recent Hong Kong graduates and those with essential work experience. <br />\n<br />\n2) Two new pathway to permanent residency for Hong Kongers in Canada and for those who want to move there. <br />\n<br />\nSource: CTV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/feds-offering-new-help-to-residents-of-hong-kong-and-canadians-living-there-1.5186013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctvnews.ca%2Fpolitics%2Ffeds-offering-new-help-to-residents-of-hong-kong-and-canadians-living-there-1.5186013&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=4aa728ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.c